Library Inflare requires NVIDIA DOCA SDK v3.2.0 installation
and was tested only on Linux Ubuntu 24.04 Kernel 6.8.0-31

Library Inflare provides CMake targets:

    find_package(inflare CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE inflare::inflare)

For direct header inclusion:

    #include <inflare/core/device.hpp>
